.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: emerald, ebony, purple, light-blue, lilac
Nationality: thai, dutch, french, turkish, indian
Beverage: mirinda, juice, 7up, sprite, iced-tea
Cigar: emeraldmaster, tiparillo, oliveros, aristoff, havana
Pet: lizard, chinchilla, rabbit, hedgehog, pony
1. Nationality:thai == Color:purple
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:rabbit
3. Nationality:dutch == Beverage:sprite
4. Color:ebony is on the left of Color:light-blue
5. Color:ebony == Beverage:juice
6. Cigar:oliveros == Pet:chinchilla
7. Color:lilac == Cigar:tiparillo
8. Beverage:7up is in the middle
9. Nationality:turkish is on the far left
10. Cigar:havana is on the left or right of Pet:lizard
11. Pet:ponys is on the left or right of Cigar:tiparillo
12. Cigar:emeraldmaster == Beverage:mirinda
13. Nationality:french == Cigar:aristoff
14. Nationality:turkish is on the left or right of Color:emerald
15. Cigar:havana is on the left or right of Beverage:iced-tea

